板","localized_name":"隐藏模板","name":"template_text","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"template_text"},"link":null},{"label":"参数值 JSON","localized_name":"参数值 JSON","name":"values_json","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"values_json"},"link":null},{"label":"参数结构 JSON","localized_name":"参数结构 JSON","name":"schema_json","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"schema_json"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"帧率","localized_name":"帧率","name":"帧率","type":"FLOAT","links":[901,902]},{"label":"时长","localized_name":"时长","name":"时长","type":"INT","links":[933]},{"label":"宽度","localized_name":"宽度","name":"宽度","type":"INT","links":[903]},{"label":"高度","localized_name":"高度","name":"高度","type":"INT","links":[904]},{"label":"Lora加速","localized_name":"Lora加速","name":"Lora加速","type":"BOOLEAN","links":[732]},{"label":"提示词","localized_name":"提示词","name":"提示词","type":"STRING","links":[936]},{"label":"文生视频","localized_name":"文生视频","name":"文生视频","type":"BOOLEAN","links":[896,897]},{"label":"参考图片","localized_name":"参考图片","name":"参考图片","type":"IMAGE","links":[905]}],"properties":{"gjj_template_params_size":[400,682],"Node name for S&R":"GJJ_TemplateParams","gjj_template_params_template":"帧率：25\n时长：5\n宽度：1280\n高度：720\nLora加速：true\n提示词：Egyptian royal in blue-and-gold headdress and high collar, white dress with golden embroidery and armbands, desert, robot soldiers in formation left and right. She walks steadily forward, head held level and gaze fixed ahead—no dipping or lowering of the head. The camera performs a single, smooth push-in only: starting in a wider shot of her, the robots, and the desert, it moves steadily forward until she is in a medium or medium-close frame, then holds. She stops, posture and head still upright, and says: “The old gods are silent. I am not.” Robot soldiers shift or march in place; sand and fabric move with the wind. No pull-back; the only camera move is the continuous push-in.\n文生视频：true\n参考图片：LTX_I2V.png","gjj_template_params_values":"{\"帧率\":\"25.0\",\"时长\":\"6\",\"宽度\":\"720\",\"高度\":\"720\",\"Lora加速\":\"true\",\"提示词\":\"埃及王室成员头戴蓝金色头饰，身着高领服饰，白色长裙上饰有金色刺绣，并佩戴臂章，身处沙漠之中，两侧有机器人士兵列队。她稳步前行，头部保持平正，目光坚定直视前方，毫无低头或俯首之态。摄像机仅进行一次流畅的推进拍摄：从她、机器人及沙漠的广角画面开始，平稳地向前移动，直至她处于中景或中近景画面，随后画面定格。她停下脚步，身姿与头部依旧挺拔，并说道：“旧神已沉寂，而我未然。”机器人士兵或稍作移动，或原地踏步；沙粒与织物随风轻扬。画面无后退镜头；摄像机的唯一动作便是持续推进。\",\"文生视频\":\"true\",\"参考图片\":\"LTX_I2V.png\"}","gjj_template_params_schema":"[{\"key\":\"帧率\",\"label\":\"帧率\",\"default\":\"25\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"INT\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"时长\",\"label\":\"时长\",\"default\":\"5\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"INT\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"宽度\",\"label\":\"宽度\",\"default\":\"1280\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"INT\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"高度\",\"label\":\"高度\",\"default\":\"720\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"INT\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"Lora加速\",\"label\":\"Lora加速\",\"default\":\"true\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"提示词\",\"label\":\"提示词\",\"default\":\"Egyptian royal in blue-and-gold headdress and high collar, white dress with golden embroidery and armbands, desert, robot soldiers in formation left and right. She walks steadily forward, head held level and gaze fixed ahead—no dipping or lowering of the head. The camera performs a single, smooth push-in only: starting in a wider shot of her, the robots, and the desert, it moves steadily forward until she is in a medium or medium-close frame, then holds. She stops, posture and head still upright, and says: “The old gods are silent. I am not.” Robot soldiers shift or march in place; sand and fabric move with the wind. No pull-back; the only camera move is the continuous push-in.\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"STRING\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"文生视频\",\"label\":\"文生视频\",\"default\":\"true\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"BOOLEAN\",\"options\":[]},{\"key\":\"参考图片\",\"label\":\"参考图片\",\"default\":\"LTX_I2V.png\",\"tooltip\":\"\",\"type\":\"IMAGE\",\"options\":[]}]"},"widgets_values":["帧率：25\n时长：5\n宽度：1280\n高度：720\nLora加速：true\n提示词：Egyptian royal in 